    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="搭建-Hexo-博客"><a href="#搭建-Hexo-博客" class="headerlink" title="搭建 Hexo 博客"></a>搭建 Hexo 博客</h2><h3 id="1-安装全局的-hexo-cli-包"><a href="#1-安装全局的-hexo-cli-包" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装全局的 hexo-cli 包"></a>1. 安装全局的 hexo-cli 包</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">npm install -g hexo-cli<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 验证安装是否成功</span></span><br>hexo -v<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-初始化-Blog-项目"><a href="#2-初始化-Blog-项目" class="headerlink" title="2. 初始化 Blog 项目"></a>2. 初始化 Blog 项目</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 选择要安装的盘符, 假设安装在 C 盘</span></span><br>cd c:<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 初始化</span></span><br>hexo init myBlog<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 检查 blog 文件夹</span></span><br>cd myBlog &amp;&amp; ls<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 检查是否能开启本地服务</span></span><br>hexo s<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 编辑器打开文件夹(待用)</span></span><br>code ./<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-创建-github-仓库"><a href="#3-创建-github-仓库" class="headerlink" title="3. 创建 github 仓库"></a>3. 创建 github 仓库</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 在 github 新建一个同名仓库</span></span><br><br>xxx.github.io (xxx为github账号的名字)<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 记录该仓库的 git 地址</span></span><br>git@github.com:xxx/xxx.github.io.git<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-配置本地项目和-github-仓库相关联"><a href="#4-配置本地项目和-github-仓库相关联" class="headerlink" title="4. 配置本地项目和 github 仓库相关联"></a>4. 配置本地项目和 github 仓库相关联</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 打开 blog 项目的配置文件 _config.yml</span></span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Site</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 网站显示的用户名</span></span><br>title: Hexo<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 副标题</span></span><br>subtitle: &#x27;&#x27;<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 描述信息</span></span><br>description: &#x27;&#x27;<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 关键词</span></span><br>keywords:<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 作者信息</span></span><br>author: Justin<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 语言设置</span></span><br>language: zh-CN<br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 时区设置</span></span><br>timezone: &#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#----------------------</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> URL</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as &#x27;http://example.com/child&#x27; and root as &#x27;/child/&#x27;</span></span><br>url: https://xxx.github.io/<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#----------------------</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Directory</span><br>post_asset_folder: true<br><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#---------------------</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Deployment</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span></span><br>deploy:<br>  type: &#x27;git&#x27;<br>  repo: https://github账号:github密码@github.com/github账号/github账号.github.io.git<br>  <br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#---------------------</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Search</span><br>search:<br> path: search.xml<br> field: post<br> format: html<br> limit: 10000<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-选择一款皮肤"><a href="#5-选择一款皮肤" class="headerlink" title="5. 选择一款皮肤"></a>5. 选择一款皮肤</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 示例: [https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid]</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 安装主题</span></span><br>npm install --save hexo-theme-fluid<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 在博客目录下创建 _config.fluid.yml，将主题的 _config.yml 内容复制进去</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 修改 Hexo 博客目录中的 _config.yml</span></span><br>theme: fluid<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建关于页面</span></span><br>hexo new page about<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 编辑博客目录下 /source/about/index.md，添加 layout 属性</span></span><br>---<br>title: about<br>date: 2020-02-23 19:20:33<br>layout: about<br>---<br><br>这里写关于页的正文，支持 Markdown, HTML<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-重新启动"><a href="#6-重新启动" class="headerlink" title="6. 重新启动"></a>6. 重新启动</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 安装提交插件</span></span><br>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 清除本地静态内容</span></span><br>hexo clean<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 生成静态博客内容</span></span><br>hexo g<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 开启本地服务</span></span><br>hexo s<br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 上传到 github 在线访问</span></span><br>hexo d<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-修改主题配置"><a href="#7-修改主题配置" class="headerlink" title="7. 修改主题配置"></a>7. 修改主题配置</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 导航栏的相关配置</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Navigation bar</span><br>navbar:<br><span class="hljs-meta">  #</span><span class="bash"> 导航栏左侧的标题，为空则按 hexo config 中 `title` 显示</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">  #</span><span class="bash"> The title on the left side of the navigation bar. If empty, it is based on `title` <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> hexo config</span><br>  blog_title: &quot;&quot;<br><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 首页副标题的独立设置</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">  #</span><span class="bash"> Independent config of home page subtitle</span><br>  slogan:<br>    enable: true<br><br>    # 为空则按 hexo config.subtitle 显示<br>    # If empty, text based on `subtitle` in hexo config<br>    text: &quot;&quot;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/guide/">更多配置文档</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
